{
  "stem": "5810.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this is where it all began, because just before it ended, and I could see maybe four or five coins left, which meant four or five months left.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the fact that we weren't eating anymore and concentration camp or not, we could fade away right there and die in that cellar and nobody would ever know.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was getting there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I decided that I needed to do something about it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So every time I went to school, I passed a cafe, and this cafe was very popular with German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They came.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was off duty.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They drank.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They got drunk.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it was very close also to a Legale Duneaux in Belgium, which is a a train station which were, of course, the favorite targets for, for the Allied bombing.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They wanted to stop them from convoys and arms shipping and all of that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had an awful lot of bombing going on in, in that particular neighborhood where we were hidden was just up the street.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this cafe was between the station and where we were hidden.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as I said, I saw them being drunk, not knowing who they were, what they were, staggering out.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said that that would be possibly a good place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they certainly had money on them too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If I needed to steal anything, this certainly would be a good place to do it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there came a time where I decided to just stay out one night and see what would happen.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the best way I can describe it today, you would call it a parking lot in the back of, of, of cafe.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it wasn't a parking lot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was just a lot.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
